column5: Vacation in style in this new 2014 Tiffin 39' RV. This coach is totally loaded and comes with all the bells and whistles: 3 luxury Beds that sleep 6, 1 1/2 baths, Indoor and Outdoor Entertainment system w/ 4 HDTVs and Dish Satellite, Full Kitchen and much more
column8: Luxury RV 2014 Tiffin QRA - 4 Slides Sleeps 6
